#

Carrot and Apple Slaw

10 min
$5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuickFresh

Description

A refreshing and crunchy slaw that combines the sweetness of apples with the earthiness of carrots, perfect as a side dish or a light lunch.

Ingredients

  • carrots: 2 large, grated
  • apple: 1 medium, grated (preferably Granny Smith or Honeycrisp)
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • honey: 1 tablespoon (optional)
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
